{
  "id": "adv_main_02_11_02",
  "title": "東京編2章27話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_studio-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……みんな、少し休憩しよう\nずっと通しで練習してたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ let's take a short break.\nWe've been practicing continuously.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "それと、すず。さっきの所、ちょっと飛ばし過ぎよ\nもっとちゃんと、周りのペースに合わせて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ Suzu. You're rushing too much in that part just now.\nPlease match the pace of those around you more carefully.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "分かっていますわ！　でも……\nどうしても、力んでしまいますの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand! But…\nI can't help but get too worked up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 24.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "次の対戦相手は、あのスリクスですし……\n瑠依さん達のかわりに、私達が頑張らないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Our next opponent is that ⅢX…\nIn place of Rui-san and the others‚ we have to do our best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんの気持ち、私も分かるよ\nトリエルがあんな目にあって、不戦敗になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ Suzu-chan.\nTRINITYAiLE was treated like that‚ and they had to withdraw…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱり悔しいし、納得出来ないもんね\nそれに、勝ち上がったスリクスが、次の相手だし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's really frustrating‚ and I can't accept it.\nBesides‚ the winner‚ ⅢX‚ is our next opponent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も、さすがに今回のは複雑かも\nトリエルのかわりに、絶対勝ちたいよねっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei feels complicated about this too.\nWe definitely want to win in TRINITYAiLE's place!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……でも、水を差すようですが……\nそれでも、相手はBIG4の一角です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…However‚ I hate to be a wet blanket…\nbut our opponent is a member of the BIG4.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちだけで勝てるほど、甘い相手じゃない\n日々の練習一回一回を、大切にしましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They are not an opponent we can easily defeat with just our feelings.\nLet's value each and every practice session.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.1666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4000,
          "startTime": 74.1666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様\n……どうしたんだ？　暗い顔して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work‚ everyone.\n…What's wrong? You all have gloomy faces.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……あの、私達\n今のままのやり方でいいんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Manager-san… um‚ are we\ndoing things the right way as they are now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "スリクスとのライブに向けて、練習の質を上げたい\nもっと他に、出来ることはないのかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to improve the quality of our practice for the live battle against ⅢX.\nI'm wondering if there's anything else we can do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 100.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そういうことならちょうど良かったよ\n実は今日から、新しく臨時コーチをお呼びしてある",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. If that's the case‚ it's perfect timing.\nI've actually invited a new temporary coach starting today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "おお～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "さすが{user}さん。仕事が早いですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As expected of Manager-san. You work fast!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、それじゃあ早速、顔合わせをしよう\n呼んで来るから、ここで待っててくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ well then let's meet them right away.\nI'll go get them‚ so wait here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7425.251261400007,
          "startTime": 118.1585845947
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "臨時コーチかぁ、どんな人なのかな？\n面白い人だと嬉しいなぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A temporary coach… I wonder what kind of person they are?\nI hope they're fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "大勝負を前にしたコーチなんだし\n厳しい人なんじゃないかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since they're a coach for a big match‚\nI wonder if they'll be a strict person.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "いずれにしても、私はこの特訓を経て\nついに、星降る奇跡へと進化するのですわ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In any case‚ after going through this special training‚\nI will finally evolve into a miracle that makes the stars fall…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.0333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4333.33333340002,
          "startTime": 140.3666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "待たせたな、みんな\n早速コーチのみなさんをお連れした……どうぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to keep you waiting‚ everyone.\nI've brought the coaches… please.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.7333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 146.5
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.66666669999,
          "startTime": 146.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "は、ハ～イ！　な、ないすちゅーみーちゅー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes! N-nice to meet you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "……え？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 153.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "わ、ワタシの名前はぁ……えっと……\nべ、ベリーグッドコーチ・ルイルイでぇ～す！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-my name is… uh…\nV-very Good Coach RuiRui~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3933.3333332999982,
          "startTime": 161.7333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "カーット！　まだ硬いわ～瑠依ちゃん！\nそんなんじゃ喜劇の舞台はまだまだ遠いよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cut! You're still stiff‚ Rui-chan!\nAt this rate‚ the comedic stage is still a long way off‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "……はい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3200.0000000000173,
          "startTime": 172.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "大変です、鈴村座長！\nルイルイの暴走で、客席が白けちゃってます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is bad‚ Suzumura-san!\nThe audience is getting bored because of RuiRui's rambling!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "なんやて！？\nこれがほんとの、シシルイルイ……な～んてな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What！？\nThis is the real ShishiRuiRui… just kidding!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
